WorkItem.Description:
Create a base template in the global namespace, e.g.

public class MyTemplateBase : TemplateBase {}

Configure razor engine to use this template:
            Razor.SetTemplateService(new TemplateService(new TemplateServiceConfiguration()
                {
                    BaseTemplateType = typeof (MyTemplateBase<>)
                }));

No template will be able to be compiled until the base template is put into a specific namespace.
